Package: phylopomp
Type: Package
Title: Phylodynamic Inference for POMP Models with Reassortment
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-04
Author: Qianying Lin [aut, cre], Aaron A. King [aut]
Maintainer: Qianying Lin <lin.5268@osu.edu>
Authors@R: c(person(given=c("Aaron","A."),family="King",role=c("aut","cre"),email="kingaa@umich.edu",comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-6159-3207")),
	  person(given=c("Qianying"),family="Lin",role=c("aut"),comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-8620-9910"))
	  )
Description: Simulation of Markov genealogy processes with multi-segment
  reassortment support. Extends the phylopomp framework to handle multiple
  genealogies representing different viral segments, enabling simulation and
  inference of reassortment events in segmented viruses such as influenza.
Depends: R(>= 4.5)
